{"tid":135620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"曾經一個月瘦7kg 你問我答","createTime":"2017-02-26T13:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T13:32:07.000Z","uid":87550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09100f58d72d6cfdce44be8f640d8a7f8f489094","tid":135620,"uid":87550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T13:12:34.000Z","msg":"冇絕食 冇食減肥藥"},{"pid":"e3475c9f0b2f89c84e875e3bfc361fe1103c6520","tid":135620,"uid":64268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T13:15:13.000Z","msg":"半年肥左10kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你點減"},{"pid":"4b64bedfdf4f8e629a93feb0881dbb800a8b9038","tid":135620,"uid":87550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T13:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>半年肥左10kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你點減</blockquote><br />\n朝早食麥皮，晏就唔好食太多，肚餓就食個蘋果，夜晚食得唔多野。平時放學會去gym，做完gym就即刻打籃球(仲要自己一個打)，平均一星期4次，但一個月後減肥團火熄左，所以就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb29999ef855cbaeebb3d36a1595528a9c195173","tid":135620,"uid":83002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T13:19:30.000Z","msg":"減咁快，果陣啲皮係咪鬆左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002c888c6d370a1f901cb35916e80b1f61f454bc","tid":135620,"uid":87550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T13:26:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>減咁快，果陣啲皮係咪鬆左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇，但有少少紋。其實我算肥壯，肌肉令到體重高。普通人以為我得六十幾ig..由82kg減到75kg，之後冇反彈過"},{"pid":"69c01dceaf01bec40997091b8fde9609afb3b335","tid":135620,"uid":38957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T13:27:07.000Z","msg":"幾高"},{"pid":"85054cd76afeee1f26e800f380b1ed5658eeb1f6","tid":135620,"uid":87550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T13:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾高</blockquote><br />\n赤腳唔知168-169"}]}